<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Carbonado2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Carbonado,</orth> vb., to cut or hack like a carbonado: <cit><quote>it is your --ed face,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.107" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 5, 107</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>eat adders' heads and toads --ed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.268" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 268</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I'll so c. your shanks,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 2, 41</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>